    <!--============ Hero Start ============-->
    <div class="breadcrumb-area" style="background:url(/assets/images/slidebg3.jpg) no-repeat top; background-size:cover; z-index:2; padding-top:45px">
        <div class="slider-mask"></div>
    </div>
    <!--============ Hero End ============-->
    <!--============ Course Detail ============-->
    <section class="pb-lg-5 pt-4 pb-4">
        <div class="container mb-4 pt-3 pb-3">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="breadcrumb_box">
                        <h5 class="text-body text-uppercase">Language Program</h5>
                        <h1 class="breadcrumb-title text-body fs-1">
                            Spoken English Course
                        </h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Left Content -->
                <div class="col-lg-8 pe-lg-3">
                    <div class="responsive-images41 rounded-4 mb-4">
                        <img src="/assets/images/spoken-english.jpg" class="rounded-4" alt="Spoken English Class ILM Academy" />
                    </div>

                    <h2 class="fs-3 text-body">Programme Overview</h2>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        ILM Academy’s <b>Spoken English Course</b> is designed to help learners improve conversational English and gain fluency in real-life situations.
                        Through <em>interactive sessions, role plays, and practical exercises</em>, students learn how to communicate with confidence.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The course covers essential aspects such as pronunciation, vocabulary, grammar usage, and listening skills. It is ideal for students, job seekers, working professionals, and anyone who wants to express themselves clearly in English.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="fs-3 text-body mb-3">Entry Requirements</h3>
                    <div class="bg-light rounded-3 p-4 mb-4">
                        <p>No advanced English knowledge required – basic understanding is sufficient.</p>
                        <p>Open to learners of all age groups who want to build confidence in speaking English.</p>
                    </div>

                    <h3 class="fs-3 text-body mb-3">Programme Structure</h3>
                    <p>The Spoken English Course covers the following key areas:</p>
                    <ul class="list-style-one">
                        <li>Conversational English for daily life</li>
                        <li>Pronunciation and accent practice</li>
                        <li>Vocabulary building with practical usage</li>
                        <li>Listening and comprehension development</li>
                        <li>Confidence building through role plays</li>
                        <li>Public speaking and group discussions</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        By the end of the course, learners will be able to confidently engage in conversations, participate in discussions, and express themselves fluently in English.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Sidebar -->
                <div class="col-lg-4 ms-auto position-relative">
                    <div class="top-0 position-sticky">
                        <a href="/apply-online" class="ht-btn ht-btn-md me-2 rounded-3 text-nowrap mb-3 w-100">Apply Now</a>

                        <div class="border rounded-3 p-4 mb-4" style="border-color:#0d4faf !important">
